parameters:
Orca Broccoli-Mayor: I can feel it... I can feel it! An
incredibly strong monster is approaching... It's sending
shivers through my orca skin!

Henchman: Hehehe... There's no monster that could be an
enemy to Orca Broccoli-Mayor in this city! Any monster that
still defies us must be incredibly stupid!

Henchman: 99% of the dark organizations in the city have
fallen under Orca Broccoli-Mayor's umbrella, promising to
pay up 50% of their earnings! Hehe, and for us who
facilitated this, we'll get a nice cut of the margin...

Orca Broccoli-Mayor: You trash...! As if I'd give you any
margin! Once we've squeezed all the protection money out of
the dark organizations, they'll all be disbanded and sent to
work in the sweatshops!

Orca Broccoli-Mayor: All that's left is to find Shark
Broccoli on the run, and his little subordinate girl.
Extract the recipe for that sweet powder from them, sell it
off... shoot a new adult video, and make even more money...
money, money...

Memimi: There's no need to search for me anymore... You
won't be shooting any new adult videos. I've come to put an
end to everything...

Orca Broccoli-Mayor: What the, little girl... it was you.
You look so different, I didn't recognize you...

Orca Broccoli-Mayor: Shark Brocc... no, little girl...? No,
a familiar monster... who are you!?

Memimi: I am the embodiment of all the monsters in Doritoku
City, born to defeat you! The strongest combined monster in
history... "The Monster Shark Duke"!!!

Orca Broccoli-Mayor: What is this pressure... It's like I'm
facing off against multiple monsters at once... What on
earth is this creature... huh, huhhh!?

Orca Broccoli-Mayor: That drill... could it be,
Drillmaid's...!? Damn it, what did you do to Meg-chan!?

Memimi: So his name was Meg-chan... This is the heart
inherited from Drillmaid! It's to awaken you from your
delusions...

Orca Broccoli-Mayor: Don't mess with me... Even that woman
betrayed me... Meg... The Monster Shark Duke... It seems
you're in dire need of a harsh punishment...

Orca Broccoli-Mayor: Step into the ring... Gathering a bunch
of weaklings won't help you. I'll show you my full power...

In the silent ring, with no gong or referee present, the
battle to determine the pinnacle of monsters was about to
begin...
